    "## Working with Local Geospatial Data\n",
    "\n",
    "### Raster Data\n",
    "\n",
    "Single-band and multi-band raster data can be loaded from local files. Here, a digital elevation model (DEM) is loaded and displayed with a terrain color scheme, and another raster is displayed with a false-color composite to highlight different features.\n",
    "\n",
    "#### Single-Band Raster Data"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "id": "179",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "url = \"https://github.com/giswqs/data/raw/main/raster/srtm90.tif\"\n",
    "filename = \"dem.tif\"\n",
    "geemap.download_file(url, filename)"
   ]
  },
