  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "287",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "#### feature.by_property\n",
    "\n",
    "Displays average precipitation by month for each ecoregion. Properties represent precipitation values for each month, allowing for visual comparison across regions by month."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "id": "288",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "ecoregions = ee.FeatureCollection(\"projects/google/charts_feature_example\")\n",
    "features = ecoregions.select(\"[0-9][0-9]_ppt|label\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "id": "289",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "geemap.ee_to_df(features)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "id": "290",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "keys = [str(x).zfill(2) + \"_ppt\" for x in range(1, 13)]\n",
    "values = calendar.month_abbr[1:]  # a list of month labels, e.g. ['Jan', 'Feb', ...]"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "id": "291",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "x_properties = dict(zip(keys, values))\n",
    "series_property = \"label\"\n",
    "title = \"Average Ecoregion Precipitation by Month\"\n",
    "colors = [\"#f0af07\", \"#0f8755\", \"#76b349\"]"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "id": "292",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "fig = chart.feature_by_property(\n",
    "    features,\n",
    "    x_properties,\n",
    "    series_property,\n",
    "    title=title,\n",
    "    colors=colors,\n",
    "    x_label=\"Month\",\n",
    "    y_label=\"Precipitation (mm)\",\n",
    "    legend_location=\"top-left\",\n",
    ")\n",
    "fig"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "293",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "![](https://i.imgur.com/6RhuUc7.png)"
   ]
  },
